name: シャルティア - Shalltear BloodFallen LORA. / Overlord - オーバーロード
description:
27th Release, シャルティア - Shalltear BloodFallen From Overlord - オーバーロード.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info, UPDATE: Example images is now Active.

Character's request, & I wanted another one with Better Quality & Flexibility.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 184+ Images that i sorted manually, at the max quality possible (Original + Official Anime Art 4K Images, Were used in the datasets) SFW+NFSW.

  • Can do Official Default Skin, Swimsuit Skin. (Perhaps Armor too).

  • He can do Original Art & Pratically Anime TV Like Shalltear BloodFallen.

  • Trained at 512x Resolution.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Work's Perfectly at Weight 1. (1.1,1.2).

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it).

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Good. (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: ShalltearV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.8-1.1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.description:
I pruned White hair & Pale Skin & Red Eyes, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((White hair, Pale Skin, Red Eyes)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: Work perfectly at Weight 1, (1.1-1.2). You can put fang, fangs prompt if you want too vampire teeth.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.
